---
title: Indian Chicken & Veg Traybake with Potatoes, Pepper & Tomatoes
description: Tray bakes are an absolute joy for busy cooks. Simply throw everything into a tray and leave it to bake for a deliciously simple meal. In this recipe, Chef Lizzie has roasted chicken drumsticks with red peppers, potatoes and onions in an Indian inspired yoghurt marinade bursting with bold flavours like ginger, turmeric and garam masala. Simple to cook, easy to prep and packed with flavour, this is a real weeknight winner.
